---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { withBase } from '../utils/url';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="Imran Ramzan — platform engineering leader in Abu Dhabi, UAE. 21 years in technology, positioning for AI infrastructure and platform engineering leadership roles in the GCC."
>
  <section class="mx-auto w-full max-w-3xl px-6 py-14 sm:py-20">
    <p class="eyebrow"># about</p>
    <h1 class="mt-3 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">About</h1>

    <div class="mt-8 space-y-6 leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        I'm Imran Ramzan, a platform engineering leader based in Abu Dhabi, UAE, with 21 years of 
        experience building the resilient, highly secure infrastructure that modern enterprise 
        workloads demand. My expertise spans secure Kubernetes at scale, multi-cloud architecture 
        (AWS, GCP, Azure), and the rigorous FinOps disciplines required to keep cloud costs optimized 
        as platforms scale.
      </p>
      
      <p>
        Currently, I serve as <strong>Head of DevOps at CallSign</strong>, a behavioral intelligence 
        SaaS platform powered by real-time machine learning and trusted by Tier 1 financial institutions, 
        aviation operators, and high-volume gaming platforms worldwide.
      </p>

      <div class="space-y-4 border-l-2 border-line pl-4 my-6">
        <p>
          <strong class="text-foreground">Scale & Performance:</strong> Scaled production Kubernetes (EKS) 
          throughput from 50 to 2,000+ TPS to support massive global traffic.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong class="text-foreground">Financial Efficiency:</strong> Rebuilt and expanded the engineering 
          team (from 6 to 14 across the UAE and UK) while slashing monthly cloud spend by ~45% on a 
          $10M+ annual budget.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong class="text-foreground">Compliance & Migration:</strong> Led a dual-cloud expansion into GCP, 
          executed complex on-premise-to-AWS migrations, and delivered SOC 2 Type II and ISO 27001 certifications 
          in highly regulated environments.
        </p>
      </div>

      <p>
        Prior to CallSign, I spent three years as a Lead Consultant with AWS Premier Consulting Partners 
        in Sydney. There, I directed large-scale enterprise cloud migrations, TCO analyses, and data center 
        exits for Tier 1 banks—contributing to CMD Solutions being named <strong>AWS Migration Partner of 
        the Year 2022</strong>.
      </p>

      <p>
        Today, I leverage deep GCC market experience to help organizations scale safely. I am open to senior 
        leadership opportunities across the UAE and wider GCC in <strong>Platform Engineering, DevOps Leadership, 
        Cloud Architecture, and AI Infrastructure</strong>.
      </p>
    </div>

    <h2 class="mt-12 text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Credentials</h2>
    <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-muted">
      <li class="flex gap-3">
        <span class="font-mono text-xs leading-6 text-accent">—</span>
        BSc Computer Science (Gold Medallist)
      </li>
      <li class="flex gap-3">
        <span class="font-mono text-xs leading-6 text-accent">—</span>
        Certified Scrum Master
      </li>
      <li class="flex gap-3">
        <span class="font-mono text-xs leading-6 text-accent">—</span>
        AZ-104 (in progress) — mandatory prerequisite for AZ-305: Azure Solutions Architect Expert
      </li>
      <li class="flex gap-3">
        <span class="font-mono text-xs leading-6 text-accent">—</span>
        AWS Migration Ambassador Foundations
      </li>
    </ul>

    <div class="mt-12 rounded-lg border border-line bg-surface p-6">
      <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-muted">
        The best way to see how I work is via the 
        <a href={withBase('/contact/')} class="text-accent hover:underline"> contact page</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>